Activated Allogeneic NK Cells Preferentially Kill Poor Prognosis B-Cell Chronic 
Lymphocytic Leukemia Cells.

Sánchez-Martínez D(1), Lanuza PM(1), Gómez N(2), Muntasell A(3), Cisneros E(2), 
Moraru M(2), Azaceta G(4), Anel A(5), Martínez-Lostao L(6), Villalba M(7), 
Palomera L(4), Vilches C(3), García Marco JA(8), Pardo J(9).

Author information:
(1)Biomedical Research Center of Aragón (CIBA), Aragón Health Research Institute 
(IIS Aragón), University of Zaragoza , Zaragoza , Spain.
(2)Immunogenetics and HLA, Instituto de Investigación Sanitaria Puerta de Hierro 
, Majadahonda , Spain.
(3)Immunity and infection Lab, IMIM (Hospital del Mar Medical Research 
